scene.message:
Queen: It's been a while,{nl}
Maki. Welcome to my{nl}
palace, {ctl0f:1} and friends.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Ch-Chisato...!!{nl}
So it really was you...?!{nl}
How could this be...!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: So it was her after all.{waitkey}{clearbox}Hey {ctl0f:1},{nl}
did Kasai's face have{nl}
that many moles?{waitkey}{clearbox}She always bragged her{nl}
skin was flawless, right...?{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Chisato!{nl}
There's a reason, right?{nl}
Is the real Queen forcing you?{waitkey}{clearbox}You being our enemy{wait_fr:32}...{nl}
that's a lie, right?{waitkey}{ret}

Queen: You're such a fool!{nl}
Me, being threatened?{nl}
Don't be ridiculous.{waitkey}{clearbox}I'm here of my own will!{nl}
Isn't the palace, this{nl}
room, lovely?{waitkey}{clearbox}An angel in black lent me{nl}
a mirror that grants any{nl}
wish - I made all this.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: You mean Aki!{nl}
Kasai, that thing{nl}
is no angel!{waitkey}Weren't you kidnapped,{nl}
anyway?{waitkey}{ret}

Queen: I thought so too{nl}
at first, but I was wrong.{waitkey}{clearbox}She was searching for a{nl}
human who could master{nl}
the mirror - and that was me.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: ...{wait_fr:32}I get that you're{nl}
the Queen, Chisato{wait_fr:32}...{nl}
so isn't that enough?{waitkey}{clearbox}Let's go home together!{nl}
Naito got hurt{wait_fr:32},{nl}
you have to be with him...{waitkey}{ret}

Queen: ...Maki{wait_fr:32}, you know{waitkey}{clearbox}I don't need Yosuke{nl}
anymore. It's not like{nl}
I even like him.{waitkey}{ret}

Queen: I never liked{nl}
Yosuke. Not from{nl}
the very start.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Liar!{nl}
You bragged about him so{nl}
much - what a great guy...{waitkey}{ret}

Queen: Still don't get it?{nl}
You really are a fool!{waitkey}{clearbox}I went out with Yosuke{nl}
because I knew that you{nl}
liked him!{waitkey}{clearbox}At first, Yosuke was the{nl}
one who liked you.{waitkey}{clearbox}But I couldn't allow that.{waitkey}After all, I'm the{nl}
prettier one - he should{nl}
have liked me, right?{waitkey}{clearbox}So I seduced Yosuke, and{nl}
that simple fool fell{nl}
head over heels for me.{waitkey}{ret}

Queen: It's no joke!{nl}
Every word is true!{waitkey}{clearbox}My paintings are better,{nl}
yet everyone fawns{nl}
over you!{waitkey}{clearbox}Honestly, I never liked{nl}
you to begin with!{waitkey}{clearbox}I'm prettier, and I've got{nl}
the talent for art too!{waitkey}{clearbox}So why is it always you{nl}
who gets the good life?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: So that's why you{nl}
stole Naito from Sonomura.{waitkey}And made the townsfolk{nl}
praise your paintings...{waitkey}{clearbox}?{wait_fr:48} Wait, Kasai.{nl}
This Sonomura is not the{nl}
same person as the{nl}
Sonomura we know.{waitkey}{ret}

Queen: Be quiet!{nl}
Outsiders should hold{nl}
their tongues!{waitkey}{clearbox}Hey Maki, deep down{nl}
you were laughing{nl}
at me, weren't you?{waitkey}{clearbox}Wearing that "I'm so{nl}
kind" face, while behind{nl}
my back, really{waitkey}you mocked me, didn't you!{waitkey}{clearbox}But I won't allow that{nl}
anymore! The me now is{nl}
better than you every way!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: With the power of{nl}
the mirror Aki{wait_fr:32}, that{nl}
girl in black, gave you,{nl}
right?{waitkey}{ret}

Queen: I said be quiet!{wait_fr:32}{nl}
...Say, {ctl0f:1},{nl}
aren't my paintings lovely?{waitkey}{clearbox}Everyone praises them.{nl}
Far better, they say, than{nl}
Maki's clumsy paintings!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Chisato, you hated{nl}
me that much...{nl}
I never knew...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Now I get why your{nl}
paintings are so lousy!{waitkey}{clearbox}Your spirit's rotten -{nl}
someone like that can't{nl}
paint anything good!{waitkey}Don't take art lightly!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Only envying Sonomura,{nl}
making no effort, and in the{nl}
end forcing others to obey{waitkey}{clearbox}through power - and you{nl}
think you've become your{nl}
ideal self?{waitkey}You're a naked emperor!{waitkey}{clearbox}No one means what they say.{waitkey}{clearbox}They only flatter you out{nl}
of fear of you!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: That's right, Kasai!{waitkey}Hurting Sonomura over some{nl}
stupid inferiority complex -{nl}
I won't forgive you!{waitkey}{clearbox}Listen, I'll say it as{nl}
many times as it takes:{nl}
your paintings are LOUSY!{waitkey}{ret}

Queen: Then go and look{nl}
at them once more!{waitkey}{clearbox}If you can't appreciate my{nl}
paintings, that's your{nl}
own fault!{waitkey}{ret}
